vote.title: Authorize the sale of one 2018 Dodge Ram 3500 pickup truck through a public auction on January 28, 2020 to Carzone Motors Esport in the amount of $25,050.00, highest bidder - Revenue: General Fund ($21,292.50) and Express Business Center Fund ($3,757.50)
